         <abstract>
            <p>This article describes scenario analysis, a technique for modeling and optimizing decisions under uncertainty. The description is informal and is oriented toward working analysts rather than theoreticians. It includes a description of the successful implementation of this method by the US Army TRADOC Analysis Center, White Sands Missile Range, NM, in a decision support system that has had extensive use in Army analysis.</p>
         </abstract>
